The paper discusses the numerical simulation of diffusion MRI signals using finite element methods, which involves solving partial differential equations. This suggests that the paper could belong to the categories of Mathematical Software (cs.MS), Numerical Analysis (cs.NA), or Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science (cs.CE). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of cloud computing resources and parallelization, which could fall under the categories of Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV) or Information Theory (cs.IT).
